{"type":"message","id":"838e393c","parentId":"e2a56921","timestamp":"2026-04-27T07:02:11.662Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Mon 2026-04-27 03:00 EDT] Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- Assistant: Hey Bobby! What's up?\n- User: [media attached: /Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/media/inbound/file_190---09682788-deac-4f5d-b15c-5c08ee900e05.ogg (audio/ogg; codecs=opus) | /Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/media/inbound/file_190---09682788-deac-4f5d-b15c-5c08ee900e05.ogg] To send an image back, prefer the m\n- Assistant: Hey Bobby! Cody here. What's going on?\n- User: [media attached: /Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/media/inbound/file_190---09682788-deac-4f5d-b15c-5c08ee900e05.ogg (audio/ogg; codecs=opus) | /Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/media/inbound/file_190---09682788-deac-4f5d-b15c-5c08ee900e05.ogg] <media:audio>\n- User: Make sure route camera is up and running now\n- Assistant: Route Camera is up and running now! **URL:** https://100.103.22.35:3443/route-camera.html The HTTPS server on port 3443 was down — just restarted it. Give it a try!\n- ## Route Camera App - 2026-04-19 Continued ### iPhone 17 Pro Max UI Fixes - Status bar: text left, 🔦 flashlight button right (justify-content: space-between) - Progress bar based on current stop number (not completed count) - Progress bar updates live on Done press, input change, and page refresh - Stop number shown in \"Go to Stop #\" input field at bottom ### Flashlight Button - Added 🔦 button in top right of status bar - Uses track.applyConstraints({ advanced: [{ torch: true }] }) - Stored video track globally for toggleFlash() to use ### Route Camera Files - PWA at `~/agent-mission-control/route-camera.html` - HTTPS server at port 3443 (route-camera-server.cjs) - URL: https://100.10\n- iPhone 17 Pro Max UI Fixes: Status bar: text left, 🔦 flashlight button right (justify-content: space-between); Progress bar based on current stop number (not completed count); Progress bar upd